show.description:
Love Me Not ek passionate romantic drama hai Rohan aur Ananya ki, jinki college se shuru hui love story, break-up, ek secret child aur 8 saal ke separation ke baad wapas takraati hai. Jab Rohan ek superstar cricketer ban kar lautta hai, toh samne aata hai ek chhupa hua sach – uska beta. Pyaar, badla, guilt aur second chances ke beech buni hai yeh kahani. Jahan pyaar aur tiff ke beech emotions har pitch se tez bhadakte hain.
Par kya sach ka samna kar ke, yeh pyaar dobara jeet payega?
